# Docs AI-first

When creating or editing docs in this repo:

1. Start with `## For agents` (when to read, apply, do-not).
2. Facts in tables/lists; checklists for verifiable steps.
3. End with source URL + `SRC-NNN` link to `SOURCES.md`.
4. One file ≈ one topic; filename = search key.
5. Do not dump full original articles — distill only.
6. Update `docs/README.md` index when adding a file.
7. Follow the template in `docs/README.md`.
